            <h2 class="article-title">Top 5 Common Household Pests and How to Control Them</h2>
            <p class="article-description">Learn about the top 5 pests that can invade your home and effective strategies for pest control and prevention.</p>

            <p class="article-intro">
                Household pests can be a nuisance and pose health risks to you and your family. In this article, we'll discuss the top 5 common household pests and provide tips on how to control and prevent infestations.
            </p>

            <ul style="list-style-type:none">
                <li>
                    <span>Cockroaches:</span>
                    Cockroaches are resilient pests that can spread diseases and trigger allergies. To control them, keep your kitchen clean, seal cracks and crevices, and use roach baits or traps strategically.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Ants:</span>
                    Ants can invade your home in search of food and water. Use ant baits, seal entry points, and maintain cleanliness to deter ant infestations.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Rodents:</span>
                    Mice and rats can cause extensive damage and contaminate food. Use snap traps or live traps, seal openings, and eliminate food sources to keep rodents away.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Bedbugs:</span>
                    Bedbugs are challenging to eradicate and can cause itchy bites. Wash bedding regularly, vacuum frequently, and consider professional pest control for severe infestations.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Termites:</span>
                    Termites can cause costly damage to wooden structures. Schedule regular termite inspections, fix moisture issues, and use termite barriers or treatments as preventive measures.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <p class="article-conclusion">
                By understanding these common household pests and implementing effective control measures, you can protect your home and family from pest infestations. For professional pest control services and expert advice, contact <a href="/contact">Expert Pest Control Services.</a>
            </p>
